title: Android : E-Commerce App using Kotlin, PHP and Paypal API
description:
Description
This course will guide you (step by step) to build a full business Android app from login screen to the payment screenBut at first, It will teach you Kotlin programming language from scratch, then you will learn how to create web services using PHP. Next you will learn how to use Kotlin in android app developmentThis course has many reach topics like Volley, Picasso and Recycler View
It’s divided into five sections:
    Kotlin Basics
    PHP and MySQL
    Android app development using Kotlin
    Build the full project
    Bonus Videos
This course is useful for IT Developers, Students or any interested person in the mobile and web development field
And if you don’t have any idea about programming basics, you can visit my channel on YouTube adenittube

Who is the target audience?

    This course is meant for IT Students, developers or any interested person in Android Apps development who are looking to develop an interactive Android Apps

Requirements

    Basic knowledge of programming
    Basic knowledge of Database

Last updated 4/2018
